OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FThousands of runners turned out for
OL,7,Fthe 36th Altra Brighton Half Marathon
OL,8,Fin windy and wet conditions, running
OL,9,F13.1 miles around the city.
OL,11,FThe event kicked off at 9.28am on
OL,12,FSunday 1 March 2026 with the Yeomans
OL,13,FToyota Wheelchair Race, followed by
OL,14,Fthe main race at 9:30am.
OL,16,FBoth started by BAFTA-nominated actor
OL,17,Fand award-winning singer Olly
OL,18,FAlexander, who ran for Team Beacon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
