OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772447794
OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FRace Direcrtor Martin Harrigan said:
OL,7,F"What an incredible weekend. The sun
OL,8,Fshone for the Youth Races on Saturday
OL,9,Fand then the rain poured and the wind
OL,10,Fblew on Sunday for the main race but
OL,11,Four runners, volunteers, supporters
OL,12,Fand sponsors were absolutely amazing."
OL,14,F"We had a record number of runners
OL,15,Fduring the race weekend with over
OL,16,F10,000 taking part.
OL,18,F"A huge thank you to everyone for
OL,19,Fmaking the Altra Brighton Half
OL,20,FMarathon the happiest half of the
OL,21,Fyear."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
