OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FBrighton-based HIV charity, The Sussex
OL,7,FBeacon Hospice is the owner of the
OL,8,Frace.
OL,10,FThe event is the charity's biggest
OL,11,Ffundraiser every year and is essential
OL,12,Fto help fund the charity's services.
OL,14,FThis year over 800 Team Beacon runners
OL,15,Fraised a record #200,000 plus for The
OL,16,FSussex Beacon Hospice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
