OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FThe race typically raises over #1
OL,7,Fmillion for charities across Sussex
OL,8,Fand the UK every year, including
OL,9,FMacmillan Cancer Support, Alzheimer's
OL,10,FSociety, Taylor-Made Dreams,
OL,11,FGrassroots Suicide Prevention, Say
OL,12,FAphasia, Venkat Memorial Trust,
OL,13,FAlcohol Change UK and local charities
OL,14,FRockinghorse, Amaze and Raystede.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
