OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FIn the wheelchair race, last year's
OL,7,Fwinner Josh Hickinbottom took first
OL,8,Fplace in the men's race with a time of
OL,9,F64 minutes and 57 seconds, followed by
OL,10,FLiam Coffill in 69 minutes 48 seconds
OL,11,Fand Rob Smith in 80 minutes and 8
OL,12,Fseconds.
OL,14,FThe women's wheelchair race was won by
OL,15,FClaudia Burrough in 70 minutes and 38
OL,16,Fseconds, followed by Mel Nicholls in
OL,17,F71 minutes and 55 seconds and Roz
OL,18,FDelap in 99 minutes and 54 seconds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
