OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772447794
OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FIn the men's race, last year's winner
OL,7,Fand course record holder Seyfu Jamaal
OL,8,Ffinished first with a time of 65
OL,9,Fminutes and 28 seconds.
OL,11,FSecond place went to Oluwatosin
OL,12,FAdedeji, who came home in 66 minutes
OL,13,Fand 21 seconds.
OL,15,FThird place went to Reuben Hoyte who
OL,16,Ffinished in 66 minutes and 41 seconds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
