PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772447794
OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FThe women's race was won by Maisie
OL,7,FTrafford, finishing in 77 minutes and
OL,8,F32 seconds, followed by Ruby Whyte-
OL,9,FWilding in 78 minutes and 14 seconds.
OL,10,FThird place went to Lucy Lavender with
OL,11,Fa time of 78 minutes and 44 seconds.
OL,13,FAlongside the elite field, thousands
OL,14,Fof charity runners took to the streets
OL,15,Fof the city, doctors from across the
OL,16,Fcountry who ran as a herd of cows!
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
