PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772447794
OL,3,CThousands brave the rain to take part
OL,4,Cin Brighton Half Marathon
OL,6,FThe Altra Brighton Half Marathon 2026
OL,7,Fstarted on Hove Lawns before sweeping
OL,8,Feast along Brighton seafront past key
OL,9,Fcity landmarks such as the i360 and
OL,10,Fthe Brighton Palace Pier before
OL,11,Fheading north past the Royal Pavilion
OL,12,Fand then on to the bracing cliff tops
OL,13,Fof East Brighton.
OL,15,FRunners then headed back to Madeira
OL,16,FDrive and then on to Hove Lagoon and
OL,17,Fthe colourful beach huts of Hove
OL,18,Fseafront, before finally heading to
OL,19,Fthe finish line on Hove Lawns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
